    </div>

    {#
      ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      ARTIST TEMPLATE SCAFFOLD
      ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      StageHaus maintains a library of reusable artist site templates
      located in /src/artist-template/.

      TEMPLATE STRUCTURE:
        /src/artist-template/
        ├── index.html        — Template preview / landing page
        ├── style.css         — Standalone CSS for template
        └── README.md         — Deployment and customization guide

      DEPLOYMENT:
        Templates deploy to GitHub Pages via the same GitHub Actions
        workflow as the main StageHaus site. Each artist gets their own
        repo forked from the template.

      CUSTOMIZATION VARIABLES (set in _data/artist.json):
        - artistName, artistGenre, artistBio
        - heroImage, logoImage, socialLinks
        - streamingLinks (Spotify, Apple Music, etc.)
        - showDates (array of upcoming events)
        - merchEnabled (boolean)

      TO ADD A NEW TEMPLATE VARIANT:
        1. Duplicate /src/artist-template/
        2. Name it /src/artist-template-[style]/ (e.g. artist-template-dark)
        3. Add to .eleventy.js passthrough copy list
        4. Update this page with the new template card below
      ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    #}

